=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽講好多人肥英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都話考之前一堂一定要返 40分基本</blockquote><br />\n咁撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇黎我要狗衝去ive了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317c8df80e33a0f7d6e019b68403dfaf5e119453","tid":307061,"uid":43309,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:35:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n有得咁讀書就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nive行規來嫁啦</blockquote><br />\n聽講ive考試就算一科fail都要比錢重新讀過，邊有咁正....</blockquote><br />\n有幾多人會肥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽講好多人肥英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都話考之前一堂一定要返 40分基本</blockquote><br />\n咁撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇黎我要狗衝去ive了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nIVE都要衝去讀，<br />\n我屌你老母笑撚到我眼水都泌出黎"},{"pid":"45798176a1ea02221d4693c2d522d33df6605f1a","tid":307061,"uid":43309,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">樓主係大陸狗黎(已自認)</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/12/161112_2d962b7cb80e281c2fa2573829c89a1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F12%2F161112_2d962b7cb80e281c2fa2573829c89a1e.jpg&h=4ed886d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個係樓主之前個名-連尼住(大佬)</span></strong></span><br />\n讀垃圾OU HD，打字用拼音。<br />\n之後俾巴打圍屌，死不悔改之餘，<br />\n仲笑鳩人讀書少，唔抵得人識打拼音！<br />\n堅稱自己係土生土長嘅香港人喎~~<br />\n樓主用拼音打字證據：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B62Ifzhk_YNaNVFfSFlRekZnclU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D0B62Ifzhk_YNaNVFfSFlRekZnclU&d=PG5mdWBhha%2BgT1dk288bnr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=147ea413\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B62Ifzhk_YNaNVFfSFlRekZnclU</a><br />\n<br />\n日期：2017-1-10<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算識打字嗰陣都要轉channel去諗嗰個字嘅蝗語點讀，再打出嚟。<br />\n點都慢過用倉頡速成就咁諗點打好撚多<br />\n除非佢本身就係蝗語channel，又或者講慣蝗語<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/12/163227_7529c4fae71b5dd7ff9beea275ef5ec9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F12%2F163227_7529c4fae71b5dd7ff9beea275ef5ec9.jpg&h=ca5c499d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本係大陸仔打啲字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唸又窩又奔，都唔知佢打乜柒！<br />\n你全家奔緊落地獄呀支那狗！！！！！<br />\n下世咪撚再落黎香港，生生世世做中蟈人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過追擊之下，終於承認自己係支那狗，<br />\n並聲稱自己永遠都唔上LIHKG<br />\n又改名-你仲唔仆街<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/15/233117_e7fca3f6eec812664dffae026e0b271d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F15%2F233117_e7fca3f6eec812664dffae026e0b271d.jpg&h=443b5ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但好景不常，經過一個月潛水又俾我見返佢！<br />\n所以只好繼續我嘅追擊行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條柒頭份人極度陰險，之前開post叫雞俾人放飛機開post起人底！<br />\n<br />\n小心呢件ptgf<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/77362/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/77362/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n仲話叫ptgf唔係叫雞喎，你咪撚玩啦！<br />\n人地唔撚so你好出奇咩？<br />\n雞都嫌棄你賤種畜生呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咁多先，希望樓主真係好好守承諾，<br />\n唔好再上黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>條賤種拎強姦慘劇黎講笑<br />\n聲稱要合法化強姦十點後外出嘅女人</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/237323/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/237323/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n你喺網上唔代表可以乜都講<br />\n你上得連登就代表你係一個人<br />\n唔該你地似返個人<br />\n認撚住條雞蟲份人係幾撚低劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ed9be2d1dee59d535413612b1f1aa1d80f0869","tid":307061,"uid":15323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T08:07:30.000Z","msg":"某d科30人讀，10個畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾HkDI"},{"pid":"ced5ec8952255f953235d0c6b199c58120267be0","tid":307061,"uid":36770,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T08:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>某d科30人讀，10個畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾HkDI</blockquote><br />\nhkdi果然係有錢仔去玩玩下嘅地方黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468bc40219e301933fa7bf6631c895457074b527","tid":307061,"uid":102641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>MK/ 偽韓 睇你讀咩</blockquote><br />\n之前上ive個網見到個演繹造型設計嘅課程，好似幾好玩，有d興趣，不過見到平均收生都係得30位，係咪代表讀完出黎等食屎架啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讀設計都係乞食科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\